title: South Africa 5 Year Note Yield
description: South Africa 5 Year Bond Yield was 9.04 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Africa 5 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 12.02 in March of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Africa 5Y.
